ns to project investment returns into the future. The specific methods used to develop expected return assumptions", "bbox": [125.0, 1289.2, 1141.7, 1311.7]}, {"text": "vary by asset category. We adjust the outcomes for the fact that plan assets are invested with actively managed funds and subject to tactical", "bbox": [125.0, 1312.1, 1131.6, 1334.6]}, {"text": "asset reallocation.", "bbox": [125.0, 1335.0, 253.3, 1357.5]}]}